  <h1>About The Arithmoi Foundation and Library</h1>
  
  <h2>The Arithmoi Foundation</h2>
  <p>The Arithmoi Foundation studies and teaches mathematics, physics, and metaphysics from an ontological standpoint. Our mission is to explore fundamental questions about the nature of reality through rigorous mathematical and philosophical inquiry.</p>
  
  <h2>The Arithmoi Library</h2>
  <p>The Arithmoi Library serves as a digital repository supporting the Foundation's mission. It provides access to a curated collection of texts, articles, and other educational materials related to our areas of study. We aim to be a valuable resource for students, researchers, and anyone interested in the profound connections between mathematics, physics, and the philosophical exploration of existence.</p>
  <p>Our digital shelves are open to all who seek to deepen their understanding of these interconnected disciplines and to engage with the foundational questions that drive human curiosity.</p>
